1. All my life I've been in serious relationships!I've always loved love and commitment even the responsibilities that come with it. But now, commitment seems scary. 
2. I wanted to marry by 24-25yr and have a family And now I don't see myself getting married anytime soon. 
3. I've been trying to become a morning person but if I wake up before 9AM, my whole day feels ruined.
4. I have a degree in B.Tech Computer Science but I've never used it..Never had to represent my degree for anything. 
5. I have had a tough childhood. And I feel the urge to end my generational/childhood trauma with me. 
6. Online shopping is therapy for me. Even if nothing fits me and I return entire package. The act of buying it in the first place is a real stress relief.
7. I have tried playing guitar but I lost interest faster than a wifi signal on a plane.
8. I do not see myself being a content creator all my life. I have bigger plans for me and for the society.
9. Sometimes I feel I'm ordinary and sometimes I feel i was meant for something bigger.
